# Local development environment variables.
#
# Copy this file to `.env` (gitignored) and fill in real values as needed.
# `.env` is loaded automatically by config/runtime.exs when you run
# `mix phx.server`, `mix test`, etc. in the dev environment — no manual
# `source` step required. Values already exported in your shell always win.
#
# Nothing is required yet for Milestone 0. Add keys here as later
# milestones need them, e.g.:
#
# STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_...
# MUX_TOKEN_ID=...
# MUX_TOKEN_SECRET=...
